data.meta_description: The Last Woman (1976) "La dernière femme" (original title) Stars: Gérard Depardieu, Ornella Muti, Michel Piccoli, Renato Salvatori, Nathalie Baye ~ Director: Marco Ferreri (Gérard Depardieu was nominated for a Cesar Award for Best Actor, 1977, and took 2nd place for Best Actor at the National Society of Film Critics Awards,1977; Won Siver Ribbon Award for Best Original Story from the Italian National Syndicate of Film Journalists 1977& nominated for 3 other awards)
